# Layer-1 control: PR-time review enforcement.
#
# Combine with a branch protection rule on `main`:
#   "Require review from Code Owners" + "Require approvals: 1"
# so an app-team PR that touches platform paths cannot merge without a
# platform-team approval, even though they have repo write access.
#
# Replace debugnin with your GitHub org or username and the team slugs with
# real teams (e.g. @kong-data-action/platform).

# Default — most files in this repo are app-team territory.
*                            @debugnin/app-team-a

# Platform tier — ONLY the platform team may approve changes here.
/manifests/platform/         @debugnin/platform-team
/argocd/                     @debugnin/platform-team
/infra/                      @debugnin/platform-team
/policies/                   @debugnin/platform-team
/.github/workflows/          @debugnin/platform-team
/.github/CODEOWNERS          @debugnin/platform-team
